Ahold Delhaize Logo
Koninklijke Ahold Delhaize N.V., commonly known as Ahold Delhaize, is a Dutch grocery retail company. Its business format includes supermarkets, convenience stores, hypermarkets, online grocery, online non-food, drugstores, and liquor stores. Its 21 local brands employ 375,000 people at 6,500 stores in 11 countries. Ahold Delhaize’s international headquarters is in Zaandam, Netherlands. Its brands are active in the Netherlands, Belgium, the Czech Republic, Greece, Luxembourg, Romania, Serbia, and the United States.
